      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i'm just trying to figure out what's actually safe right now. i've read online that aspirin is a really good fever reducer. if i just give him a small dose, is that going to be a huge problem or is it mostly just an issue for older kids? i just really need to get this fever down so he can sleep.",
